 o FEATURES
 ----------

  This class provide you a  new  button  class  with  new  features  for  the
  bgui.library.

  With it you can SET: Labels, Labels-colors, Frame-colors on the fly.

  Special mode allow to have the size of button smaller  than  the  text
  width, and another mode allow to justify labels.

  See ButClass.doc for mode informations.


